posts.post_content: Looking to buy t206 cards! Lots preferred and the worse condition the better

I started a T206 Binder set last April.  Took off like I was shot from a Cannon.  Constantly coming across large lots of 20 plus cards. 

I'm now 357/520 and things seem to be slowing down. 

Using a pop report from PSA/SGC compiled by another user here on Net54 , I have concentrated my buying power on the top 100 cards (82/100) and now that has gotten slow I have turned to the 101-200 list. 

Good luck on the Binder build.  
I have about a dozen doubles I'm looking to trade. 

Hit me up if interested. 

Billy
